<main class="container py-4">
  <nav aria-label="breadcrumb">
    <ol class="breadcrumb">
      <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="/app">Rhodes ROSA style demo</a></li>
      <li class="breadcrumb-item active" aria-current="page">ROSA dialogs</li>
    </ol>
  </nav>

  <header class="mb-4">
    <p class="text-uppercase text-body-secondary fw-semibold mb-2">Rhodes ROSA style demo</p>
    <h1 class="h2 mb-2">ROSA dialogs</h1>
    <p class="text-body-secondary mb-0">Живые диалоги на стандартной Bootstrap modal-разметке, стилизованные под ROSA.</p>
  </header>

  <section class="card mb-4">
    <div class="card-header fw-semibold">Вызов диалогов</div>
    <div class="card-body d-flex flex-wrap gap-2">
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#rosaDialogOneButton">One button</button>
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-rosa-secondary-blue" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#rosaDialogTwoButtons">Two buttons</button>
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-rosa-secondary-blue" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#rosaDialogThreeButtons">Three buttons</button>
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-rosa-secondary-blue" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#rosaDialogIcons">Icons stack</button>
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-rosa-secondary-blue" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#rosaDialogCode">Code dialog</button>
      <button type="button" class="btn btn-dark" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#rosaDialogDark">Dark dialog</button>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="card mb-4">
    <div class="card-header fw-semibold">Используемая структура</div>
    <div class="card-body">
      <p class="text-body-secondary mb-0">Каждый пример ниже использует стандартные классы modal, modal-dialog-centered, modal-content, modal-header, modal-body и modal-footer. ROSA меняет только визуальный слой: размеры, radius, overlay, отступы и кнопки.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <a class="btn btn-outline-secondary" href="/app">
    <i data-feather="arrow-left" class="me-1"></i>
    Назад на главную
  </a>
</main>

<div class="modal fade rosa-dialog" id="rosaDialogOneButton" tabindex="-1" aria-labelledby="rosaDialogOneButtonTitle" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog modal-dialog-centered">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h5 class="modal-title rosa-dialog-title" id="rosaDialogOneButtonTitle">Разрешить уведомления?</h5>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p class="rosa-dialog-text">Будьте в курсе новых обновлений внутри приложения.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer rosa-dialog-actions">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-bs-dismiss="modal">Action</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

